Throughput (Output Tokens per Second)

Higher is better. Measures how many tokens the system can generate per second.

Time to First Token (TTFT)

Lower is better. Time from request start until the first token is generated.

Inter-Token Latency (ITL)

Lower is better. Time between consecutive tokens during generation.

Request Latency

Lower is better. Total time from request start to completion.
